longBusinessSummary: Stillfront Group AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, designs, develops, markets, publishes, and sells digital games in Europe, North America, the Middle East and North Africa, and the Asia-Pacific. Its games portfolio include Supremacy 1914, Call of War: World War 2, Adult Coloring Book, Goodgame Empire, BitLife, Conflict of Nations: World War 3, Goodgame Big Farm, Sunshine Island Adventure Farm, Jawaker, Warhammer, Shishinogotoku, 3 Kingdoms STG Sangokuhaosenki, Empire, and Imperia. The company's games portfolio include Ellen's Garden Restoration, Too Hot to Handle 2 NETFLIX, Winked, Parchis Club, Hollywood Story, Big Farm: Mobile Harvest, Shakes & Fidget, Word Collect Word Puzzle Game, Trivia Star, Albion Online, Home Design Makeover, Property Brothers Home Design, The Grand Frontier, Nida Harb 3, and Ludo Club. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
